high_descs: Turn around and go in to the kitchen to the countertop with the microwave on it.
Pick up the black mug next to the microwave.
Turn left and go to the kitchen sink.
Put the mug in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out.
Turn around and go to the countertop with the microwave.
Put the mug on the countertop next to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed Mug on the CounterTop.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the countertop microwave oven.
Take the mug from the counter top.
move around and walk towards the sink.
Open the tap and wash the mug in the sink and take the mug out.
Turn around and go back near the oven placed on the countertop.
Place the mug on the countertop near the oven.
anns.task_desc: Take the mug, wash it and place it again on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight, turn right towards the counter top
Pick up mug from the counter top
Turn left and head straight, turn around and then proceed to turn left towards the sink
Place mug inside sink and then take it out
Turn around and head straight, turn around then make a turn right towards the counter top
Place mug on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Washing mug on the sink and placing it on counter top
